tes/ko/nikola-kovachev-1.html|accessdate=2009-10-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=11177|title=Nikola Kovachev - national football team player|website=eu-football.info}}</ref>\n\nHe coached [[PFC Hebar Pazardzhik|Hebar Pazardzhik]] and [[PFC CSKA Sofia|CSKA Sofia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hebarfc.com/nikola_kovachev.php|title=\u041d\u0435\u043e\u0444\u0438\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u0435\u043d \u0441\u0430\u0439\u0442 \u043d\u0430 \u0424\u041a \u0425\u0435\u0431\u044a\u0440 \u041f\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u0434\u0436\u0438\u043a|first=Vladislav|last=Lazarov|website=www.hebarfc.com}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n===International===\n;Bulgaria\n*[[Football at the Summer Olympics|Olympic]] Bronze Medal: [[Association football at the 1956 Summer Olympics|1956]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Bulgaria football squad 1956 Summer Olympics}}\n{{Bulgaria Squad 1962 World Cup}}\n{{PFC CSKA Sofia managers}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kovachev, Nikola}}\n[[Category:1934 births]]\n[[Category:2009 deaths]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:Bulgaria international footballers]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian football managers]]\n[[Category:PFC Botev Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:PFC CSKA Sofia players]]\n[[Category:1962 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 1952 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 1956 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 1960 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic footballers of Bulgaria]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Bulgaria]]\n[[Category:People from Blagoevgrad]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in football]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n[[Category:Macedonian Bulgarians]]\n[[Category:PFC CSKA Sofia managers]]\n[[Category:PFC Hebar Pazardzhik managers]]\n\n\n{{Bulgaria-footy-defender-stub}}\n{{Bulgaria-Olympic-medalist-stub}}\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2013}}\n{{refimprove|date