8', \uc1a1\ud61c\uad50\uc640 \uacb0\ubcc4 \uc2ec\uacbd \ud1a0\ub85c?|date=8 March 2011|website=Asia Economy|language=ko}}</ref> \n|-\n| \"That Man\" || [[Secret Garden (South Korean TV series)#Soundtrack|''Secret Garden'' OST]]\n|<ref name=thatman /> \n|}\n\n==Ambassadorship==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year \n! Event\n! Ref. \n|-\n| 2011 || PR ambassador of Hyundai Motors' \"Hyundai Grandeur\"\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/03/07/2011030700385.html|title=Hyun Bin Donates Hyundai Grandeur to UNICEF|date=7 March 2011|website=The Chosun Ilbo|language=ko}}</ref>\n|- \n| 2013 || PR ambassador of Kia Motors' \"The New K5\"\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.hankyung.com/business/2013/06/14/0809011/kia-motors-releases-the-new-k5?setct=print&popup=1|title=Kia Motors Releases The New K5|date=14 June 2013|website=Korea Economic Daily}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014 || Promotional ambassador of Incheon Asian Games \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/07/04/2014070401197.html|title=Hyun Bin Picked to Promote Incheon Asian Games|date=4 July 2014|website=The Chosun Ilbo}}</ref>\n|- \n| 2016 || Promotional ambassador of Gwangju Biennale\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2016/05/25/2016052501102.html|title=Hyun Bin to Promote Gwangju Biennale|date=25 May 2016|website=The Chosun Ilbo|language=ko}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year \n! Award\n! Category \n! Nominated work \n! Result \n! Ref. \n|-\n| rowspan=2| 2004\n| [[MBC Entertainment Awards]] || Special Award, TV Actor category ||  ''[[Nonstop 4]]'' || {{won}} \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://joynews.inews24.com/php/news_view.php?g_menu=700999&g_serial=134501|title=\uc774\uacbd\uaddc, 2004 MBC '\ubc29\uc1a1\uc5f0\uc608\ub300\uc0c1' \ub300\uc0c1 \uc218\uc0c1|date=30 December 2004|website=Joy News|language=ko}}</ref> \n|-\n| [[MBC Drama Awards]] || Best New Actor || rowspan=2|  ''[[Ireland (TV series)|Ireland]]'' || {{won}}  \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2004123020180638852|title=\uace0\ub450\uc2ec, '2004 MBC \uc5f0\uae30\ub300\uc0c1' \ub300\uc0c1 \uc218\uc0c1|date=31 December 2004|website=Star News|language=ko}}</ref> \n|-\n| rowspan=4| 2005 \n|  [[41st Baeksang Arts Awards|41st]] [[Baeksang Arts Awards]] || [[Baeksang Arts Awards for Best New Actor (TV)| Best New Actor (TV)]] || {{nom}}||\n|-\n| rowspan=3|  [[MBC Drama Awards]] \n| Top Excellence Award, Actor || rowspan=3| ''[[My Lovely Sam Soon|My Name Is Kim Sam-soon]]''  ||{{won}}||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hancinema.net/tv-networks-hand-out-awards-4836.html|title=TV Networks Hand Out Awards|date=1 January 2006|website=Hancinema|publisher=The Korea Times}}</ref>\n|-\n| Popularity Award || {{won}}||rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hani.co.kr/arti/culture/entertainment/91905.html|title=\uae40\uc120\uc544, MBC \uc5f0\uae30\ub300\uc0c1 \uc218\uc0c1|date=31 December 2005|website=Hankook Ilbo|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Couple Award <small>with [[Kim Sun-a]]</small> ||  {{won}} \n|-\n| rowspan=5| 2006 \n|  [[42nd Baeksang Arts Awards|42nd]] [[Baeksang Arts Awards]] \n| [[Baeksang Arts Awards for Most Popular Actor (Film)| Most Popular Actor (Film)]] || ''[[A Millionaire's First Love]]'' || {{won}} \n| <ref>[http://twitchfilm.com/news/2006/04/42nd-baeksang-awards-nominations-winners.php 42nd Baeksang Awards Nominations + Winners] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120908060719/http://twitchfilm.com/news/2006/04/42nd-baeksang-awards-nominations-winners.php |date=2012-09-08 }}. ''[[Twitch Film]]''. 14 April 2006.</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=4|  [[2006 KBS Drama Awards|KBS Drama Awards]]\n| Excellence Award, Actor  || rowspan=5| ''[[The Snow Queen (TV series)|The Snow Queen]]'' ||{{nom}} \n| \n|- \n| Popularity Award || {{won}} \n|rowspan=3|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kbs.co.kr/drama/2006award/|title=2006 KBS Drama Awards|website=KBS|language=ko}}</ref